.DT
query_zones
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_zones

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_zones -  This method returns the move zones for the specified room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * query_zones(string room)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^room%^RESET%^ - the room to get the zones for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the array of move zones for the room
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the move zones for the specified room.  It will
load the room if it is not available in the map handlers cache.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_short()

.EP

